      • hmXTranslatedValueSeries

        public java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Number> hmXTranslatedValueSeries
        The hm X of Translated Series. When a Serie is translated, the original is hided, and we add a translated series in the chart and the table view with a name beginning by T_ . If we translate a T_xxx series it keeps this name to avoid cumulating T_T_ prefixes. If we reset the chart the T_xxx are deleted and we re-shown all hided series Tthe key of the map is the name of the original serie
